材质包这个位置assets\minecraft\models\item
新建名为diamond_axe文本，修改后缀为json，打开并输入以下，保存
{
  "parent": "item/handheld",
  "textures": {
    "layer0": "items/diamond_axe"
  },
  "overrides": [
    { "predicate": {"damaged": 0, "damage": 0}, "model": "item/diamond_axe"},
    { "predicate": {"damaged": 0, "damage": 0.0006402048655569782}, "model": "block/custom/a"},
        { "predicate": {"damaged": 0, "damage": 0.0012804097311139564}, "model": "block/custom/b"},
    { "predicate": {"damaged": 0, "damage": 0.0019206145966709346}, "model": "block/custom/c"},
    { "predicate": {"damaged": 1, "damage": 0}, "model": "item/diamond_axe"}
  ]
}复制代码
然后材质包assets\minecraft\models\block\custom位置下，新建a.json，b.json，c.json

a.json输入如下，保存。b.json和c.json同理{
    "parent": "item/handheld",
    "textures": {
        "layer0": "items/custom/a"
    }
}复制代码

材质包assets\minecraft\textures\items\custom下放入贴图a.png，b.png和c.png

最后，游戏里获取a
/give @p minecraft:diamond_axe 1 1 {Unbreakable:1b}复制代码

获取b
/give @p minecraft:diamond_axe 1 2{Unbreakable:1b}复制代码

获取c
/give @p minecraft:diamond_axe 1 3{Unbreakable:1b}复制代码


1.13的give格式...
/give @p minecraft:diamond_axe{Unbreakable:1b,Damage:1s}复制代码



大概就是这样...

把那个json进行修改，例子{
    "parent": "builtin/generated",
    "textures": {
        "layer0": "custom/cb/cbico"
    },
    "display": {
        "thirdperson_righthand": {
            "rotation": [ -90, 0, 0 ],
            "translation": [ 0, 1, -3 ],
            "scale": [ 0.55, 0.55, 0.55 ]
        },
        "firstperson": {
            "rotation": [ 0, -135, 25 ],
            "translation": [ 0, 4, 2 ],
            "scale": [ 1.7, 1.7, 1.7 ]
        }
    }
}复制代码display下定义thirdperson_righthand(第三人称右手), thirdperson_lefthand(第三人称左手), firstperson_righthand(...), firstperson_lefthand, gui, head, ground, 或fixed

rotation为旋转，translation为位移，scale为各轴大小
https://minecraft-zh.gamepedia.com/%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B

scale变大完后，修改rotation和tralslation的数值进行显示调整，游戏内F3+T重新加载材质。
或者你可以用blockbench软件，进行可视化修改。
